01:07:26.060 --> 01:07:28.060
Right.

01:07:32.060 --> 01:07:34.060
Were you allowed days off

01:07:34.060 --> 01:07:36.060
for personal reasons?

01:07:36.060 --> 01:07:38.060
You know, like funerals

01:07:38.060 --> 01:07:40.060
or things like that. Could you have

01:07:40.060 --> 01:07:42.060
a day off for that?

01:07:42.060 --> 01:07:44.060
Yes, we did. They did allow it, but they had

01:07:44.060 --> 01:07:46.060
to make sure it was

01:07:46.060 --> 01:07:48.060
for the reason, like if I had to go to hospital

01:07:48.060 --> 01:07:50.060
or I had to

01:07:50.060 --> 01:07:52.060
take my daughter somewhere,

01:07:52.060 --> 01:07:54.060
like dentists, they did give it to us.

01:07:54.060 --> 01:07:56.060
And were you paid for that day?

01:07:56.060 --> 01:07:58.060
I cannot remember

01:07:58.060 --> 01:08:00.060
that at all.

01:08:00.060 --> 01:08:02.060
I think I was

01:08:02.060 --> 01:08:04.060
deducted, but I can't really

01:08:04.060 --> 01:08:06.060
remember.

01:08:12.060 --> 01:08:14.060
So,

01:08:14.060 --> 01:08:16.060
I'm coming to the end now.

01:08:16.060 --> 01:08:18.060
Did you enjoy working in the factory?

01:08:18.060 --> 01:08:20.060
I did really enjoy.

01:08:20.060 --> 01:08:22.060
Wherever I did

01:08:22.060 --> 01:08:24.060
go, I did enjoy those

01:08:24.060 --> 01:08:26.060
times. Were you ever bored?

01:08:26.060 --> 01:08:28.060
Oh, if it was

01:08:28.060 --> 01:08:30.060
a new job and I didn't

01:08:30.060 --> 01:08:32.060
like it, I'd find a way of getting

01:08:32.060 --> 01:08:34.060
around it to make

01:08:34.060 --> 01:08:36.060
it happier. I found

01:08:36.060 --> 01:08:38.060
a way of dealing with it.

01:08:38.060 --> 01:08:40.060
What do you mean, a new job in the factory now?

01:08:40.060 --> 01:08:42.060
Yes, yes, because

01:08:42.060 --> 01:08:44.060
they would put me on a polishing machine

01:08:44.060 --> 01:08:46.060
and I broke a rib

01:08:46.060 --> 01:08:48.060
and I was struggling to

01:08:48.060 --> 01:08:50.060
use the machine. But I had

01:08:50.060 --> 01:08:52.060
to leave and go to the

01:08:52.060 --> 01:08:54.060
doctors without them knowing. They did not

01:08:54.060 --> 01:08:56.060
know I left. And got

01:08:56.060 --> 01:08:58.060
a note and told them

01:08:58.060 --> 01:09:00.060
in a note that I needed to be

01:09:00.060 --> 01:09:02.060
taking off the machine for a while.

01:09:02.060 --> 01:09:04.060
But as soon as two, three

01:09:04.060 --> 01:09:06.060
days, they put me back on it.

01:09:06.060 --> 01:09:08.060
But that was

01:09:08.060 --> 01:09:10.060
a happy job that wasn't.

01:09:10.060 --> 01:09:12.060
But I tried to

01:09:12.060 --> 01:09:14.060
mind over matter.

01:09:14.060 --> 01:09:16.060
So did they change your jobs?

01:09:16.060 --> 01:09:18.060
Well, they did

01:09:18.060 --> 01:09:20.060
when they took over.

01:09:20.060 --> 01:09:22.060
And they tried to, this

01:09:22.060 --> 01:09:24.060
one man tried to do it in front of

01:09:24.060 --> 01:09:26.060
Doug Atwood, which he wasn't

01:09:26.060 --> 01:09:28.060
happy about. He made me go

01:09:28.060 --> 01:09:30.060
to a section and

01:09:30.060 --> 01:09:32.060
Doug would come out and he'd say,

01:09:32.060 --> 01:09:34.060
Why are you here, Anne?

01:09:34.060 --> 01:09:36.060
And I'd tell him, Mr Groke,

01:09:36.060 --> 01:09:38.060
get your chair, go back

01:09:38.060 --> 01:09:40.060
and stay there. I want

01:09:40.060 --> 01:09:42.060
you there. Soliding.

01:09:42.060 --> 01:09:44.060
And then Mr Groke would say,

01:09:44.060 --> 01:09:46.060
Why is she back here? And there would

01:09:46.060 --> 01:09:48.060
be a difference because they weren't getting on.

01:09:48.060 --> 01:09:50.060
Did you prefer

01:09:50.060 --> 01:09:52.060
soldering to other things? Oh, yes, yes.

01:09:52.060 --> 01:09:54.060
That was your favourite? Yes, because I could

01:09:54.060 --> 01:09:56.060
get my,

01:09:56.060 --> 01:09:58.060
you know

01:09:58.060 --> 01:10:00.060
an artist drawing

01:10:00.060 --> 01:10:02.060
and painting, I could

01:10:02.060 --> 01:10:04.060
do that sort of thing. You know,

01:10:04.060 --> 01:10:06.060
I put my mind to

01:10:06.060 --> 01:10:08.060
how it should look. It was

01:10:08.060 --> 01:10:10.060
creative. Oh, yes.

01:10:10.060 --> 01:10:12.060
And you were

01:10:12.060 --> 01:10:14.060
in a way

01:10:14.060 --> 01:10:16.060
helping to create

01:10:16.060 --> 01:10:18.060
that piece of jewelry. Object.

01:10:18.060 --> 01:10:20.060
Because there were some

01:10:20.060 --> 01:10:22.060
you had to make yourself, which

01:10:22.060 --> 01:10:24.060
like the bird, you had to make

01:10:24.060 --> 01:10:26.060
the breast

01:10:26.060 --> 01:10:28.060
and you had to do it at the right

01:10:28.060 --> 01:10:30.060
weight because of

01:10:30.060 --> 01:10:32.060
the weight of the bird.

01:10:32.060 --> 01:10:34.060
You'd give it

01:10:34.060 --> 01:10:36.060
to a big of a breast and

01:10:36.060 --> 01:10:38.060
they'd come back and they'd say, this is not good,

01:10:38.060 --> 01:10:40.060
this is not the right weight. But you

01:10:40.060 --> 01:10:42.060
had to make sure there was no

01:10:42.060 --> 01:10:44.060
lines or any holes

01:10:44.060 --> 01:10:46.060
in it because when the polishers got old

01:10:46.060 --> 01:10:48.060
of it, it would show

01:10:48.060 --> 01:10:50.060
up. So do

01:10:50.060 --> 01:10:52.060
you think it was a very skilled job?

01:10:52.060 --> 01:10:54.060
I do, yes. I loved it.

01:10:54.060 --> 01:10:56.060
I loved that.

01:10:58.060 --> 01:11:00.060
So looking back,

01:11:00.060 --> 01:11:02.060
how do you feel about

01:11:02.060 --> 01:11:04.060
the time you worked

01:11:04.060 --> 01:11:06.060
in the factory?

01:11:06.060 --> 01:11:08.060
I wish I could have

01:11:08.060 --> 01:11:10.060
been a supervisor

01:11:10.060 --> 01:11:12.060
and I loved

01:11:12.060 --> 01:11:14.060
teaching girls.

01:11:14.060 --> 01:11:16.060
And I had

01:11:16.060 --> 01:11:18.060
a supervisor who had no patience

01:11:18.060 --> 01:11:20.060
and she'd throw the work at you

01:11:20.060 --> 01:11:22.060
and the tray and say, do

01:11:22.060 --> 01:11:24.060
it again. Because she did that to me on the

01:11:24.060 --> 01:11:26.060
first day I was there.

01:11:26.060 --> 01:11:28.060
And I'd go in the toilet crying

01:11:28.060 --> 01:11:30.060
because I needed the job badly.

01:11:30.060 --> 01:11:32.060
And she'd follow me in. She would

01:11:32.060 --> 01:11:34.060
follow us on our chat

01:11:34.060 --> 01:11:36.060
and she'd understand she had gone too

01:11:36.060 --> 01:11:38.060
far. But I knew that

01:11:38.060 --> 01:11:40.060
those girls, when they came,

01:11:40.060 --> 01:11:42.060
would feel the same way as

01:11:42.060 --> 01:11:44.060
I did. So I

01:11:44.060 --> 01:11:46.060
used to try and find a way

01:11:46.060 --> 01:11:48.060
of helping them.

01:11:48.060 --> 01:11:50.060
I had more time to help them.

01:11:50.060 --> 01:11:52.060
You'd be sympathetic then?

01:11:52.060 --> 01:11:54.060
Yes, yes.

01:11:54.060 --> 01:11:56.060
Whether they took any notice

01:11:56.060 --> 01:11:58.060
sometimes because some of them didn't want

01:11:58.060 --> 01:12:00.060
the job, they just wanted the money.

01:12:00.060 --> 01:12:02.060
Would you say

01:12:02.060 --> 01:12:04.060
you enjoyed those years

01:12:04.060 --> 01:12:06.060
at the factory? Oh yes.

01:12:06.060 --> 01:12:08.060
And I did the same in the rugby

01:12:08.060 --> 01:12:10.060
club as well because I was a barmaid

01:12:10.060 --> 01:12:12.060
and I took over

01:12:12.060 --> 01:12:14.060
on days that I

01:12:14.060 --> 01:12:16.060
was in charge. I was in

01:12:16.060 --> 01:12:18.060
charge! And I used to

01:12:18.060 --> 01:12:20.060
employ girls

01:12:20.060 --> 01:12:22.060
to come and help me. And I

01:12:22.060 --> 01:12:24.060
had some wonderful girls.

01:12:24.060 --> 01:12:26.060
And that job I would have

01:12:26.060 --> 01:12:28.060
loved to have taken on as a

01:12:28.060 --> 01:12:30.060
stewardess, but they

01:12:30.060 --> 01:12:32.060
didn't want that.

01:12:32.060 --> 01:12:34.060
They had some man that came

01:12:34.060 --> 01:12:36.060
from Australia

01:12:36.060 --> 01:12:38.060
who was a rugby player, gave

01:12:38.060 --> 01:12:40.060
him £15,000 to

01:12:40.060 --> 01:12:42.060
run the club and he

01:12:42.060 --> 01:12:44.060
absconded. And I thought, well, what did

01:12:44.060 --> 01:12:46.060
you do that for when I was offering

01:12:46.060 --> 01:12:48.060
for £12,000 a year?

01:12:48.060 --> 01:12:50.060
Was that too much

01:12:50.060 --> 01:12:52.060
I asked for?

01:12:52.060 --> 01:12:54.060
Oh well, thank you

01:12:54.060 --> 01:12:56.060
very much. Hey, that's my pleasure.

01:12:56.060 --> 01:12:58.060
Thank you.

